    <item>
      <title>Before installing YubiKey&#39;s ykman software</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/yubikey/EN_Install_all_dependencies/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 12:30:21 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/yubikey/EN_Install_all_dependencies/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;before-you-install-ykman&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Before you install ykman&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#before-you-install-ykman&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You will need to have the following onboard&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;apt install gnupg2 scdaemon pcscd pip pipx &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;GnuPG — The Universal Crypto Engine&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;scdaemon - Smartcard daemon for the GnuPG system&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;pcscd - PC/SC Smart Card Daemon&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;pipx - execute binaries from Python packages in isolated environments&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>YubiKey GPG Guide</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/yubikey/NL_yubikey_gpg/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 1970 01:33:40 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/yubikey/NL_yubikey_gpg/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hier is een &lt;strong&gt;duidelijke, complete en professionele uitleg&lt;/strong&gt; voor het &lt;strong&gt;instellen van PGP op een YubiKey&lt;/strong&gt;.&#xA;Ik houd het overzichtelijk maar technisch correct.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;-instellen-van-pgp-op-een-yubikey-gpg--yubikey&#34;&gt;&#xA;  🔐 Instellen van PGP op een YubiKey (GPG + YubiKey)&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#-instellen-van-pgp-op-een-yubikey-gpg--yubikey&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Dit is de &lt;strong&gt;standaard, best-practice workflow&lt;/strong&gt; om PGP veilig op een YubiKey te gebruiken.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-installeer-benodigde-software&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;strong&gt;1. Installeer benodigde software&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#1-installeer-benodigde-software&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;linux&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Linux&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#linux&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt install gnupg2 scdaemon pcscd yubikey-manager yubikey-personalization&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo systemctl enable --now pcscd&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;macos-via-homebrew&#34;&gt;&#xA;  macOS (via Homebrew)&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#macos-via-homebrew&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew install gnupg yubikey-personalization yubikey-manager&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew services start pcscd&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-maak-een&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;strong&gt;2. Maak een &lt;em&gt;offline master key&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#2-maak-een&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Dit is de belangrijkste stap.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>YubiKey install ykman from git</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/yubikey/EN_yubikey_install_ykman/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 1970 01:33:40 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/yubikey/EN_yubikey_install_ykman/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;-installing-the-latest-ykman-advanced-methods&#34;&gt;&#xA;  🔧 Installing the Latest &lt;code&gt;ykman&lt;/code&gt; (Advanced Methods)&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#-installing-the-latest-ykman-advanced-methods&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;For advanced users, there are several ways to install the &lt;strong&gt;latest development version&lt;/strong&gt; of YubiKey Manager (&lt;code&gt;ykman&lt;/code&gt;) directly from source.&#xA;Choose the method that best fits your workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;1--install-ykman-in-a-python-virtual-environment-recommended&#34;&gt;&#xA;  1. 📦 Install &lt;code&gt;ykman&lt;/code&gt; in a Python Virtual Environment (Recommended)&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#1--install-ykman-in-a-python-virtual-environment-recommended&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This keeps the installation &lt;strong&gt;isolated&lt;/strong&gt; from your system Python and avoids conflicts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
